{"tid":1240950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:45:45.000Z","uid":100517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf6143a21675bff3c03fc554bbee4ad1e52b281","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"我發夢見到12號嗰日我喺現場其中一個急救/物資站做急救員，見到有好多醫療物資同人員但係好少傷者埋到嚟，想問下：<br />\n<br />\n1.嗰日係唔係無乜人知啲急救物資站喺邊度？<br />\n2.啲醫療物資又有幾多去到有需要嘅人手上？<br />\n3.前線除咗物資之外究竟後排嘅人仲可以點幫手？<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到嗰日溝通做得非常不足（急救站之間幾乎無任何聯絡，除咗同附近嘅人玩收買佬之外，完全唔知邊度需要啲乜）,喺度想同大家say sorry&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n另外我覺得前排嘅人可以俾下意見，點樣support會更好，更有效率，俾後排嘅人參考下。<br />\n<br />\n不論係食緊放題嗰陣定係而家抖緊。<br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人都想聽，因為只有前線最清楚前線嘅需要。亦希望大家之間可以減少誤會，因為都見到幾個post前排有啲怨氣&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n天佑我城<br />\n（第一次開post, sorry for 1999)"},{"pid":"6ed667f544a30e7fefced5d2677f71a2ac682bb8","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"994526dbc5847a311c71e85badeadcf0af1aba59","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5386db7ece12e5d193fc5e7d9106bd9f2bba3ce4","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"407d92bec8679e53f0347247be86fd156a5a455d","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"發夢12號嗰日喺hot zone做first aid，大部分中招嘅人都係hot zone清洗搞掂，得些小嚴重區會退到cold zone post處理<br />\n<br />\ncold zone first aid唔洗咁多人，但要好清楚物資放邊，等人黎補給，甚至叫人排人鏈將物資由cold zone傳去hot zone"},{"pid":"adb7469da90346e964b7e0c5ae483f9e9b2b2f48","tid":1240950,"uid":257397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"經驗之談<br />\n五年前發左個夢，個夢講我知除左大穫食到應曬，義士們都唔太會退去後面，佢地會留到真係頂唔順先會退。<br />\n今年再發夢，我唔想佢地再係前面咁辛苦死頂，直接帶住first aid 做埋前線，反而可以幫到更多義士。當然好唔合符first aid 原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb115da00a60fe7551a54f3c2d8d0c8539f5294","tid":1240950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"醫療站 係咪話去過日本幫手 個位巴打個到？ 遠東後面？"},{"pid":"35ac0cfd86b01f3c1346cef9d64228dd872432b6","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"407d92bec8679e53f0347247be86fd156a5a455d","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"發夢12號嗰日喺hot zone做first aid，大部分中招嘅人都係hot zone清洗搞掂，得些小嚴重區會退到cold zone post處理<br />\n<br />\ncold zone first aid唔洗咁多人，但要好清楚物資放邊，等人黎補給，甚至叫人排人鏈將物資由cold zone傳去hot zone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"人鏈呢招唔錯，下次可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbacd6601fd8038627073866e3c8279b5420c51c","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ac0cfd86b01f3c1346cef9d64228dd872432b6","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"407d92bec8679e53f0347247be86fd156a5a455d","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"發夢12號嗰日喺hot zone做first aid，大部分中招嘅人都係hot zone清洗搞掂，得些小嚴重區會退到cold zone post處理<br />\n<br />\ncold zone first aid唔洗咁多人，但要好清楚物資放邊，等人黎補給，甚至叫人排人鏈將物資由cold zone傳去hot zone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"人鏈呢招唔錯，下次可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"其實一直都有用"},{"pid":"f549322803379c48a3addbe6dfaee9ef0ad2bcd5","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bb115da00a60fe7551a54f3c2d8d0c8539f5294","tid":1240950,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"醫療站 係咪話去過日本幫手 個位巴打個到？ 遠東後面？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"夢入面好似係夏慤道大家樂嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20150ec938893625c07eb7376fcd89e1409e9ad1","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbacd6601fd8038627073866e3c8279b5420c51c","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ac0cfd86b01f3c1346cef9d64228dd872432b6","tid":1240950,"uid":100517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"407d92bec8679e53f0347247be86fd156a5a455d","tid":1240950,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"發夢12號嗰日喺hot zone做first aid，大部分中招嘅人都係hot zone清洗搞掂，得些小嚴重區會退到cold zone post處理<br />\n<br />\ncold zone first aid唔洗咁多人，但要好清楚物資放邊，等人黎補給，甚至叫人排人鏈將物資由cold zone傳去hot zone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"人鏈呢招唔錯，下次可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"其實一直都有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"我喺個夢入面見到仲有成差唔多一百支生理鹹水堆咗喺急救站，大部分一放催淚煙就拎唔走，所以係咪應該分散啲物資？"}]}